WEBVTT

00:00.203 --> 00:02.101
<i>Previously on "The Mist"...</i>

00:02.125 --> 00:05.460
Every act of destruction
is an act of creation.

00:05.529 --> 00:07.829
That is why the Black Spring is here.

00:07.898 --> 00:09.130
If I see you touching her,

00:09.199 --> 00:10.780
I will put a bullet

00:10.827 --> 00:13.225
in whatever body part
you touch her with.

00:13.280 --> 00:15.370
- What can I do?
- Find me a room.

00:15.439 --> 00:18.640
- Hey! You can't do this!
- Watch me.

00:18.708 --> 00:20.053
What do you think they're gonna say

00:20.077 --> 00:21.677
when they know you have your own supply?

00:22.874 --> 00:24.273
Help!

00:24.342 --> 00:26.020
It was Alex. I saw her
running away from here.

00:26.044 --> 00:27.810
- No one could love you.
- Alex loves me.

00:27.879 --> 00:29.323
Until she finds someone
that can fuck her.

00:29.347 --> 00:31.414
- I did.
- Adrian, please. Please, don't.

00:31.483 --> 00:33.349
I'm sorry.

00:35.487 --> 00:37.020
Adrian, what happened?

00:37.088 --> 00:39.122
He's dead.

